## example

```dataviewjs
for (let group of dv.pages("#todo").groupBy(p => p.genre)) {
    let a = 1;
    dv.header(3, group.key);
    dv.table(["Name", "Time Read", "Rating","No"],
        group.rows
            .sort(k => k.rating, 'desc')
            .map(k => [k.file.link, k["time-read"], k.rating, a++]))
}

```

